Testing New Generation Framework
Unit Testing Framework
Used to design test cases
Open Source - Freely available
Available in form of Jar File
Java Unit Testing Framework(Only Applicable for Java)
Lot of annoations are there
User can define sequence and Priority
Define Dependencies, Grouping
Most important is Data Provider Feature
TestNG is TDD(Test Driven Development) framework
No main method required for TestNG
Execution Sequence(STCMT)
1.@BeforeSuite
2.@BeforeTest
3.@BeforeClass
4.@BeforeMethod
5.@Test
6.@AfterMethod
7.@AfterClass
8.@AfterTest
9.@AfterSuite
